{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "唐大在黄河小轩被暗杀身亡，邓玉函与一名黑衣女子交手。萧秋水赶到一剑挑开对方面纱，发现她是唐大之妹唐方。唐方解释潜入剑庐寻兄，却见大哥已死。朱侠武认出唐方身份，揭露她是唐门最美丽的年轻高手。观鱼阁传来怒吼，康出渔服张临意之药后病情恶化，疑被人在酒中下毒。振眉阁传来惨叫，张临意被刺杀身亡，凶手是其意想不到之人。老夫人现身，揭示其身份为名将狄青养母狄太夫人，朱侠武曾在其麾下任职。萧西楼安排防守，与朱侠武轮流值守。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "text": "“是她杀的！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“唐大侠是怎么死的？”",
      "tone": "沉痛",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“事情的经过是怎样的？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "text": "“唐大侠自己服了几颗药丸后，便静下来闭目调息，我便在一旁护法，心里是想：浣花剑庐，铁壁铜墙，谁能闯得进来？……没料就在这时，一名黑衣人飞过。迎面就是给我一剑！”",
      "tone": "叙述",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "text": "“这人剑法虽高，但却似因逃避仓皇，剑快但架沟稍呈凌乱，来得突然，但布局未周，所以这一剑，我还接得下。”",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "text": "“我们交手二招，他抢主动在先，故得上风，但他三剑不下，立时逃遁，我急忙追出，没几步便猛想起唐大侠正在疗毒，旁人惊扰不得，是以立即赶回，却不料见这黑衣人工站在唐大侠身边，而唐大侠己中暗算身亡，我看……便是这女了害死唐大侠的！”",
      "tone": "指控",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "text": "“这位姑娘与你交手，有没有用过剑？”",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "text": "“没有。”",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这姑娘身上没有剑，谁都可以看出来，唐大侠却是死于剑伤。”",
      "tone": "推理",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“就算不是元凶，也可能是同谋。”",
      "tone": "悻然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“绝对不可能是同谋。”",
      "tone": "斩钉截铁",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“因为她就是唐方，唐大的嫡亲妹妹，唐门最美丽的年轻一代高手。”",
      "tone": "断然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这种身前发镖、身后命中的‘子母回魂镖’，除唐家子弟之外，是没有人能发得出来的。”",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“朱叔叔。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "text": "“萧伯伯。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "“唐侄女，我们错怪了你，你不要生气。”",
      "tone": "歉意",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "“唐……唐姑娘，你是怎么……怎么赶来这里的呢？”",
      "tone": "腼腆",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我知悉大哥在这里，特地赶来，看见权力帮的人包围着剑庐，所以潜了进来，干脆悄悄地溜进内院，想吓大哥一跳——我来时，大哥的血还流着，那时，这位兄台还在与那黑衣人作战，我方才定过神来，他也不打话，见我就杀。然后……然后又来了这位……这位。”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "“是我不好。……我先动手的。”",
      "tone": "歉疚",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "“我也……也冒犯了姑娘。”",
      "tone": "歉意",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“秋水撩开面纱，玉函便不以二对一，很好；秋水一招得刊，而不进击，更好。你们都很好，以后武林，少不了你们的大号。”",
      "tone": "赞许",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“可惜唐大侠……”",
      "tone": "喟然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不好！”",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“劫生，住手！”",
      "tone": "喝止",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“劫生，发生什么事？”",
      "tone": "叱问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“爹他……”",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“怎么康兄……”",
      "tone": "惊愕",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“那药……那药！”",
      "tone": "嘶喊",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“什么药！”",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“张老前辈的药？！”",
      "tone": "惊觉",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“张老前辈说康师伯的毒中得很怪异，他也查不出来；这药是要送酒，烫热了才能服的。”",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“药浸酒中时，你有没有出去过？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“有。我去小解了一次。”",
      "tone": "呆愣",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“回来后才给令尊服食？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "惶然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“朱兄是认为康世侄出去时，别人在酒里下毒？”",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“张前辈怎会在府上？是否可靠？”",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“实不相瞒，老夫人就在府中。”",
      "tone": "郑重",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“老夫人？”",
      "tone": "吃惊",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是老夫人。”",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“原来是老夫人。”",
      "tone": "喃喃敬慕",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“张前辈实是老夫人的护卫。”",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“那张前辈应绝无问题。”",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“然则下毒的人是谁呢？”",
      "tone": "蹙眉",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“你留在这里守护！”",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他就是张老前辈？”",
      "tone": "轻呼",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“难道，难道有人的剑，比张前辈的剑还快！”",
      "tone": "苦思",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不是。”",
      "tone": "断然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“不是？”",
      "tone": "侧问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不是因为敌手剑快，而是张前辈意料不到对方会出剑。”",
      "tone": "斩钉截铁",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不过，对方的剑确实也不慢，否则就算猝然发动，也杀不了张前辈。”",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“而且，而且也是与我们非常，非常熟悉的人。”",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这人杀了唐大侠，又向康先生下毒，更猝击玉函、秋水，又刺杀张前辈——这个人！”",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“振眉阁里？”",
      "tone": "惊叫",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“这位大叔，何必如此礼重？”",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“未将侠武，曾在大人麾下侦骑队参任纵组副使将。”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“是朱铁心吧？”",
      "tone": "恍然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“正是铁心，小人不知老夫人还记得小人。”",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“现下又不是在行军之中，青儿也不在，铁心何必如此多礼，不必什么大人小人的！”",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“小人不敢，小人敢问狄大将军安好！”",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不可：汉臣不过常人也。他跟你们都是一样，都想为国为民做点事。他只是一个堂堂正正的大宋人，他的大志也也正是诸位心中的大事，还得仗列位匡扶协力。他要的是为国为民大丈夫，有忠有勇好兄弟，而不是摇尾乞怜的亡国奴才！”",
      "tone": "正色",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“青儿战于广南，平乱贼党，侬智高要捕捉老身与儿媳，以乱青儿作战之心。我与儿媳，一走成都，一赴开封。我这一把年纪，生死并不足惜，只怕扰乱了青儿的斗志，说什么也得逃离奸人魔掌的。”",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“狄将军为国杀敌，累了太夫人，我等虽非军人，自当为国保护老夫人，但仍屡令夫人受惊吓，实是惶愧！”",
      "tone": "惶愧",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "text": "“萧大侠客气了，叨扰贵派，以致权力帮大举进犯，涂炭生灵，这是老身的罪孽。”",
      "tone": "歉疚",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“大将军勇赴沙场，在下未及万一；照顾太夫人，乃义不容辞之事，只要在下有一口气在，定必死而后已，只是……只是这干来犯之徒，非同泛泛，权力帮除勾结西夏番子外，还与奸相吕夷简等暗下私通，实力甚厚。”",
      "tone": "慷慨",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“正是。这一路上，我也遭到了屡次的埋伏，可恨身无长技，不然也想杀得几个卖国贼子，以祭先烈。……这一路上，倒是张妈护我得紧。”",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“禀告大夫人……张……张妈他于适才为人所杀……”",
      "tone": "蹭然",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_furen",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“适才我在里面，忽听外面搏剑之声，因守护大夫人，不敢离房，没料……”",
      "tone": "自责",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“张妈不是女人，我是知道的。他是狄青的结义兄弟，特地乔装以保护我，要我唤他作‘张妈’”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我这条老命不足惜，但我死了，青儿会觉得他连累了老身，此心影响他的斗志甚巨。”",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“记得西夏番将遣人来告，青儿已被杀死，我和媳妇儿一颗眼泪也没掉，不是不怕，而是不信，山河未复，狄汉臣不会死，也不能死！”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“可是蛮兵若抓到我，我就不会让他们把我活着送到前线去，我宁死亦不可乱青儿之心，亦不能作人质劝降宋军！”",
      "tone": "刚烈",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "text": "“狄太夫人，我们绝不让您落于敌人之手！”",
      "tone": "慷慨",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“好孩子！青儿此时应在昆仑关、否则你真该见他一见！”",
      "tone": "慈蔼",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“大夫人请安心，张老前辈的后事，我们自会妥为办理。”",
      "tone": "郑重",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“夜深了。”",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“看来一切很平静。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“以水淹火一役，权力帮已失主力。”",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“看来如此。”",
      "tone": "认同",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“现在我们一定要做一件事。”",
      "tone": "郑重",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“睡觉？”",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“睡觉！”",
      "tone": "斩钉截铁",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你我之间，只有一人能睡。”",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“你先睡，我后睡。”",
      "tone": "谦让",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "speaker_name": "朱侠武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好。三更后，我醒来，你再睡。”",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": "char_zhu_xia_wu",
      "text": "“一言为定。三更我叫你。”",
      "tone": "约定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_lou",
      "speaker_name": "萧西楼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“张老前辈剑合阴阳，天地合一。康出渔剑如旭日，剑落日沉。海南剑派辛辣急奇，举世无双。孔扬秦剑快如电，出剑如雪。辛虎丘剑走偏锋，以险称绝……只可惜这些人，不是遭受暗杀，就是中毒受害，或投敌卖国，怎不能一齐复我河山呢！”",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 8
    }
  ],
